Insider Activity


Individual




Arnold S. Barron



Mr. Arnold S. Barron is Independent Director at Dollar Tree, Inc. He is on the Board of Directors at Dollar Tree, Inc.
Mr. Barron was previously employed as Independent Director by rue21, Inc., Chief Operating Officer & Executive Vice President by The Marmaxx Group, Senior VP & General Manager-Merchandising by T.J. Maxx, Inc., and Group President & Senior Executive Vice President by The TJX Cos., Inc.



