Company Overview of Dollar Tree, Inc.



SnapshotPeople 




OverviewBoard MembersCommittees



Executive Profile
Arnold S. Barron  Director, Dollar Tree, Inc.AgeTotal Calculated CompensationThis person is connected to 2 Board Members in 2 different organizations across 2 different industries.See Board Relationships69$285,000
Background

		Mr. Arnold S. Barron served as an Executive Advisor of The TJX Companies, Inc. since November 1, 2008. Mr. Barron served as Senior Executive Vice President and Group President of The Tjx Companies Inc. from March 29, 2004 to November 1, 2008. He was responsible for T.K. Maxx, Corporate E-Commerce Services, the New York Buying Office and a new position overseeing long-range Distribution and Logistics Strategy for TJX. Since 1979, Mr. Barron promoted to a series of increasingly ... responsible positions within The Marmaxx Group and TJX's Corporate group. Mr. Barron served as an Executive Vice President and Chief Operating Officer of The Marmaxx Group from 2000 to March 29, 2004 and served as Senior Vice President, Group Executive of TJX Companies Inc. from 1996 to 2000, Senior Vice President, General Merchandise Manager of the T.J. Maxx Division from 1993 to 1996, Senior Vice President, Director of Stores from 1984 to 1993 and held various store operation positions with TJX from 1979 to 1984. He has been an Independent Director at rue21, Inc. since November 20, 2009. Mr. Barron has been Director of Dollar Tree, Inc. since March 2008.Read Full Background




